name: OKSA Handbag - Nude
description:
This leather handbag is crafted using quality vegetable tanned cow leather that improves with use and ages beautifully. The bag consists of hand cut leather straps put together by silver-plated rivets, resulting in an original structure that resembles a nest. 

Combining functional design and traditional leather techniques, the end result is a unique and innovative product that aims to become an extension of the personality of the wearer.

Inside it carries a drawstring cotton bag. Available in other colours on request.

Size: 28cm x 20cm.

* Genuine leather is a natural product, thus each hide has unique markings and a character of its own.

Shipping & Delivery
=================
All the products are shipped worldwide from Spain

Spain: 1/2 working days
EU countries: 4/5 working days. 
Rest of the world: 6/7 working days.

name: TUULI Shoulder Bag - Nude
description:
This convertible leather bag can be used as a shoulder bag, crossbody or hand clutch. It is 100% hand crafted using a single piece of quality vegetable tanned cow leather and silver-plated brass hardware.

The bag consists of a detachable/adjustable shoulder strap, one inside pocket and a fold over and tuck in tag closure.

No stitching was used in the construction of this bag, resulting in a unique and functional origami-inspired box bag.

Size: 21cm(L) x 5.5cm(W) x 16cm(H)

* Genuine leather is a natural product, thus each hide has unique markings and a character of its own.

Shipping & Delivery
=================
All the products are shipped worldwide from Spain

Spain: 1/2 working days
EU countries: 4/5 working days. 
Rest of the world: 1/2 weeks.
